Markets We ServeNovelis / Markets We Serve


A Catalyst for Innovation
Novelis scientists work closely with our​ customers to help design some of today’s most advanced and sophisticated aluminum products. From more efficient cars to more sustainable packaging and beautifully crafted electronics, Novelis aluminum is helping to shape your world.










Beverage Can
Novelis is the largest producer of aluminum beverage can sheet and the world’s largest recycler of used beverage cans (UBCs), recycling roughly 60 billion UBCs each year.
READ MORE




 










Automotive
Novelis helps drive the creation of some of the world’s most innovative cars, trucks and high speed rail systems.
READ MORE




 






Architecture and Building
Thanks to Novelis aluminum, the stunning architectural beauty and sustainable design of some of the world’s most renowned buildings shape how we live, work and play.
READ MORE




 






Consumer Goods
From smart phones, laptops and tablets to high-definition flatscreen TVs, the light weight, durability and attractive finishes of today’s specialty aluminum sheet are working their way into consumer goods at every turn.
READ MORE




 






Lithography & Printing
Since the creation of the earliest printing press, the ability to effectively communicate to mass audiences has changed the world, and today is no exception.
READ MORE




 






Industrial Aluminum Applications
Novelis aluminum is an essential material for a wide variety of industrial and household applications, ranging from refrigerators, stoves, heating and air conditioning equipment to high-visibility road signs.
READ MORE




 






PAE Casthouse Equipment
Novelis PAE combines the know-how of equipment manufacturing with the extensive operating experience and research and development capabilities.
READ MORE





























