Novelis Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 10:47 AM ET
Metals and Mining

Company Overview of Novelis Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Novelis Inc. manufactures and sells aluminum rolled products. The company operates through North America, Europe, Asia, and South America segments. It manufactures aluminum sheet, light gauge, and foil products, as well as recycles aluminum. The company's products are used in the beverage and food cans, electronics, containers and packaging, automotive and other transportation, architectural, foil and technical products, lithographic sheet, and other industrial applications. It sells its products through direct sales force, as well as distributors. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia. Novelis Inc. is a subsidiary of AV Metals Inc.


3560 Lenox RoadSuite 2000Atlanta, GA 30326United StatesFounded in 200411,450 Employees



Phone: 404-760-4000

