Novelis - Wikipedia





















 






Novelis

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Novelis Inc.)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Novelis





Type

Subsidiary


Industry
Metals, manufacturing, recycling


