novelis inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Metals & Mining
Sub-Industry: Base Metals
Novelis Inc. produces and sells aluminum rolled products. The Company offers aluminum sheet and light gauge products primarily for use in beverage cans, automotives, consumer electronics, and foil markets.




