 Novelis Inc.  

 

 



Novelis Inc.


Share


 







  
  
  Novelis is the global leader in aluminum rolled products and aluminum recycling. Novelis supplies premium aluminum sheet products to the automotive, transportation, packaging, construction, industrial and electronics markets. Novelis is a subsidiary of Hindalco Industries Limited, one of Asia’s largest integrated producers of aluminum and a leading copper producer and a division of the Aditya Birla Groupa multinational conglomerate based in Mumbai, India.
NAICS 331, Primary Metal Manufacturing
Date of Pledge: March 2014
  

 












 



 

 
 

 















